<doc id="732993" wikidata="Q4532458" url="?curid=732993" title="Sune Eriksson">
<text>Sune Eriksson (born 19 March 1939) is a politician who served as the Premier of Åland Islands, an autonomous and unilingually Swedish territory of Finland.

*Minister of social affairs and environment 2001–2003
*Speaker, Ålands lagting (Åland parliament) 1999–2000
*1st deputy speaker 1995–1999
*Premier (lantråd) 1988–1991
*Member of Ålands lagting (the Åland parliament) 1979–1999

